You need to redirect both STDERR and STDOUT to a file. Which of the following charactersequences accomplishes this task?
A)  2>
B)  2>&1
C)  2+1
D)  +2+1
B
B. The character sequence shown in option B is the correct sequence to redirect bothSTDERR and STDOUT. Of the other options shown, option A will redirect only STDERR.The other options shown are not valid.
